		"Id": "mechdef_devastator_DVS-3D",
		"Name": "Devastator",
		"Details": "Developed after a series of tests by the NAIS, the Devastator DVS-3D is an interesting take on the combination of Psychological and \"real\" warfare.  It was noted in the run up past the 3040s that mechwarriors would often eject after taking lots of fire, regardless of how damaged the mech was.  NAIS technicians, psychologists, and engineers worked together put the most shots on target.  LRMs were determined as in-effective because the smokey trail of their motors made them easy to spot.  Psychologically only an invisible weapon system would work.  Hence, x AC/2s are the primary weapon system on this mech.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>Pafftek Industries Sub-mod</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_devastator"
	},
